                    </div>
                    <span>Many books have been written about success and self help, but this book is at the top of the heap. The techniques are very powerful and they do work. The mirror technique is especially powerful. This technique enables one to develop a hypnotic and magnetic personality. The author writes in this book that the methods must not be misused or there will be a rebound of evil. This is no idle warning. I found that Hitler used the mirror technique to develop a hypnotic personality. The mirror method gives one the power to use suggestion to influence other people. This is how Hitler could overtake Germany and people would kill at his command. No doubt Hitler was a master at the mirror technique. This is an incredible book that also shows how to use the powers of visualization to gain great power. Nothing I wrote is an exageration. This book is awesome. I have seen the results for myself. Please heed the authors warning and do not use the book for evil. If you do you do you will surely suffer the consequences. A great, great book.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">My own long-term experiment with this book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
